      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Some content in the display is adaptive and will show the
most relevant information depending on the current system status.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To navigate the display it is possible to:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Press icons to open pages.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Press the gray bars to maximize/minimize content on a page.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Scroll on a page or in a content window.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Use the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Home icon</uicontrol> to return to the home
screen.</p>
